    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Albert Burns, Robert Sproat, and Audrey Sproat collection of Laura (Riding) Jackson correspondence, 1968-1977. #6300. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
